                          "name": "oBNoteT",
                          "fill": "#A8A8A8",
                          "content": "Side-by-side breaks the chat's vertical reading rhythm and pushes the input box below the fold whenever 3+ leaders spawn. Option A keeps a single conversation spine — the parent acts as a workflow event, the children are inspectable on demand. Sticky context bar + collapsible children scale to N leaders without UI redesign.",
